Deep Photo Style Transfer 论文笔记

Posted on 2021-11-13

Introduction

在neural style transfer基础上加入了一个regularization term保证了：

A transformation model that is locally affine in colorspace.

是optimization-based的方法。

Motivation

因为以往的方法：

when both the input and reference images are photographs, the output still exhibits distortions reminiscent of a painting.

作者希望style transfer的结果是

broad and faithful

能

remove these painting-like effects by preventing spatial distortion and constraining the transfer operations to happen only in color space.

故提出该方法，这里提一下作者提到的photorealistic style transfer的两大挑战：

  • Structure preservation:很好理解，就是不能改变content image的structure information，作者自己也解释为：

    we seek a transformation that can strongly affect image colors while having no geometric effect.

  • Semantic accuracy and transfer faithfulness: 举个例子，当图片由太多元素组成时（e.g., building, sky），在进行style transfer时，我们希望

    the appearance of buildings should be matched to buildings, and sky to sky

    最后作者方法是：

    incorporate a semantic labeling of the input and style images into the transfer procedure so that the transfer happens between semantically equivalent subregions and within each of them.

Poposed Methods

方法很简单，一个regularization term，一个semantic label。这里先介绍一下neural style transfer的背景。

Neural Style Algorithm

Transfer the reference style image S onto the input image I to produce an output image O by minimizing the objective function:

其中L是convolutional layer的total number，l表示第l-th convolutional layer。Fl表示l-th层的输出，其feature maps的数量为Nl，每个feature map在vectorized之后的长度是Dl，所以Fl输出的大小为Nl * Dl，然后Gram Matrix定义为：

Gram matrix is defined as product between the vectorized feature maps.

Gram Matrix，即第二个loss是用来衡量the style的。

Photorealism regularization

作者提到：

Our strategy is to express this constraint not on the output image directly but on the transformation that is applied to the input image.

因为要描述photorealistic space是一个未被解决的问题，所以在input image是photorealistic的情况下，我们只要保证transformation不会破坏photorealistic的property就行了。

作者将这个描述为：

seek an image transformation that is locally affine in color space, that is, a function such that for each output patch, there is an affine function that maps the input RGB values onto their output counterparts.

最后用到了Matting Laplacian

They describe a least-squares penalty function that can be minimized with a standard linear system represented by a matrix Mi that only dependes on the input image I.

其中，Vc[O]表示output image O 在channel c的vectorized version（vectorized version就是指把2-dimension给拉成1-dimension），Mi只和input image I有关，I vectorized之后有N个pixel，Mi的大小就是 N X N。具体的计算，这里没有放出来，可以去参考一下。

Augmented style loss with semantic segmentation

A limitation of the style term is that Gram matrix is computed over the entire image.

于是作者加入了additional channel，作为一个mask

和上面的Ls相比，就是加入了个mask（有点alpha通道的感觉）。不过这个M下标为(l,c)是什么意思呢？明白了，一个mask可能对应一个label，那么这里的C指的是mask的数量，如果就一个mask，那么就是对每层的feature F(l, c)乘以一个mask。

Discussion

有收获，这个regularization term可以尝试加到loss里面，来保证photorealistic，对于semantic label，其实CLIP本身也能用于生成semantic label吧，比如我们想要对car做style transfer，那我输入一个car，用optimize-based方法，看哪一个区域的像素变化最大，说明那里就是和car强烈相关的区域。

因此，只要CLIP能够提供和text prompt符合的color distribution，然后用local affine transformation进行约束，再用CLIP本身生成semantic label优化style loss。理论上可行，可以一试。
